body:
- fix issue#110: missing rules change because no js cache was updated after rule added/deleted.
- support custom install path
- add GitHub issue template
- add some log items in nginx.conf
- fix some typo issues
- remove dir `docs/api`, more docs [here](http://orange.sumory.com)

- new plugin: signature auth plugin
- add configuration template
- add new plugin `property_rate_limiting` which extracts `property` with `extractor` module as the limit key.

- Add `Makefile`
- Support orange start/stop/restart/reload/store with resty-cli
- Support `orange store` to init database
- Break Change: move orange.conf under conf

- Remove examples dir
- Add plugin: key auth
- Add plugin: rate limiting
- Add more specific API docs
- Fix some small problems

- HTTP Basic Auth Plugin Support
- Restful API for thirdparty usages
- A new extractor called `template extractor`
- File store removed
- Dashboard separated with independent api
